<doc id="523392" wikidata="Q2662182" url="?curid=523392" title="Prime Minister of the Sahrawi Arab Democratic Republic">
<text>The prime minister of the Sahrawi Arab Democratic Republic is the head of government of the Sahrawi Arab Democratic Republic (SADR), a government in exile based in the Sahrawi refugee camps of Tindouf, Algeria. The post of the prime minister has been held by Bouchraya Hammoudi Bayoun since 13 January 2020.

